        "System.Description": "<div><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\">Create pop-up prompt for the banker to ask the customer if\nthey would like to receive their disclosures electronically.</span><br></div><div><font face=\"Calibri, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.6667px;\">The message should read:<p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,sans-serif;\">&quot;If\nyou have been certified for sending electronic Disclosures, please ask the\ncustomer if they would like to receive their disclosures\nelectronically.&quot;&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\">The pop-up message should appear just before the Print Documents screen in the Account Opening flow.</span></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\">The only purpose of\nthis pop-up window is to present a message. The prompt presents the text with\nan </span><i style=\"font-size:11pt;\">OK</i><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"> button at the bottom which, when selected, escapes the banker out\nof the prompt such that the prompt is no longer displayed, and the banker can\nproceed through the workflow as currently designed with no affect from the\nprompt.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p style=\"margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt;font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot;,sans-serif;color:#002060;\">&nbsp;</span></p></span></font></div>",
        "Microsoft.VSTS.Common.AcceptanceCriteria": "<div>CBT Validated/et 03.31.20</div>",
